name: Lunacloud Java SDK
body:
### Welcome to Lunacloud Java SDK.
This is the Lunacloud Java SDK page, where you'll find resources for aiding in developing Lunacloud services related Java applications.

### Authors and Contributors
So far, this is a fork from @aws _AWS Java SDK_ [1] tailored to work with _Lunacloud Storage_ service [2]. In the future, it's expected the integration of other _Lunacloud_ services, such as _Lunacloud Server_ [3] management.

  [1]: https://github.com/aws/aws-sdk-java "AWS Java SDK"
  [2]: http://www.lunacloud.pt/en/cloud-storage "Lunacloud Storage"
  [3]: http://www.lunacloud.pt/en/cloud-server "Lunacloud Server"
